series of CD-Rom products called Justis Official Press Releases. It combines
the EU's Rapid database of documents and communiques (from 1985) on
economic, trade, science and technology and other sectors with the Hermes
database of more than 35,000 UK government press releases.
It costs Pounds 587.50 a year and is updated quarterly. News released
between updates is available from an on-line computer link.
